locality: Special Reserve Anjanaharibe-Sud, around camp 2. Dense evergreen mid altitude forest.

SAVA, Andapa, Doany, Andranomilolo. Forêt dense humide de moyenne altitude située environ 13 Km à l'Ouest du village d'Andranopositra. Récoltés avec R. Razakamalala, D. Ravelonarivo, Landrie (Doany) & José (Ambalamanasy). Echantillons préservés en alcool.
National Park Montagne d'Ambre, along trail from Grand Lac to Pic d'Ambre, near summit. Dense evergreen mid altitude forest, rainfall 4000 mm/year.
National Park Marojejy, along east trail to summit of Marojejy between camp 2 and 3. Evergreen low altitude forest.
Ambanizana, Masoala Peninsula. Along Androka River S. of MBG house. Plants preserved in alcohol.
